{"id":"c5553f1d-e99a-4f5e-aeb1-9f414be78d4c","level":0,"callsign":"Guardian","name":"Arthur","player_name":"","status":"Active","dead":false,"text_appearance":"<p>Xandar is a man of very average stature and build, he is not too tall or muscular but he is not wimpy either. Arthurs most distinguishable trait is his shining silver hair which makes standout in any crowd. He also sports blue eyes though one was lost during a run in with a wild boar as a child. Arthur has also gained some tech as a pilot but prefers to wear subtle and light equipment to match his robes. He also carries with him a small ceremonial blade from his adopted guardian to reminder of home. </p>","notes":"","history":"<p>All was peaceful in <strong>Upheamia, </strong>a home for those with an affinity for magic such as <strong>Arthur</strong> and his sister. Both were orphans raised by the leader of an order of priests known as the <strong>The Iron Convocation </strong>where they became priests in training. Life was good until the village was attacked by a group known simply as <strong>The Order Of Ash </strong>destroying their home. Both Arthur and his sister tried to use a special teleport spell to escape along with a small group of women and children. However due to a lack of skill they messed it up teleporting them far into the future. Stranded in an unfamiliar world Arthur was then attacked by a group of thugs before he was saved by a pilot. The pilot took him in and entered him into the academy where Arthur demonstrated proficiency in medical support and survival. Now Arthur separated from his sister has become a pilot and hopes to one day find her and the others who have been lost.</p>","quirks":[],"current_hp":9,"background":"PRIEST","resistances":[],"mechs":[{"id":"f0ec769c-7540-4cd9-a020-db116193f94b","name":"Anomaly","notes":"","gm_note":"","frame":"mf_standard_pattern_i_everest","active":false,"current_structure":4,"current_move":4,"boost":0,"current_hp":14,"overshield":0,"current_stres